t addons have in common is that they’re 100% free. So you can try any WoW addon you like and see which one creates the game experience that’s best for you.\n\nThe most important thing to keep in mind with these addons for World of Warcraft is to have fun with them. So try all of them out until you find your favorite ones."])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"5:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"game-page-root\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L1f\",null,{\"game\":{\"id\":1,\"slug\":\"wow\",\"name\":\"World of Warcraft\",\"description\":\"$20\",\"modsCount\":21793,\"downloadsCount\":9212111954,\"createdAt\":1435584904313,\"iconUrl\":\"https://media.forgecdn.net/avatars/63/986/636148993918069601.png\",\"tileUrl\":\"https://media.forgecdn.net/game-box-art/1_b6157245-1827-4f52-82ac-2b8b67d38521.jpg\",\"logoUrl\":\"https://media.forgecdn.net/game-logos/wow.png\",\"coverArtUrl\":\"https://media.forgecdn.net/game-covers/1_953f85b1-1a49-456b-be44-657ea7fb7e5d.jpg\"},\"categories\":[{\"id\":1028,\"name\":\"Warrior\",\"slug\":\"warrior\",\"isClass\":false,\"classId\":1,\"parentId\":1020},{\"id\":1018,\"name\":\"Action Bars\",\"slug\":\"action-bars\",\"isClass\":false,\"classId\":1,\"parentId\":1},{\"id\":1002,\"name\":\"Auction \u0026 Economy\",\"slug\":\"auction-economy\",\"isClass\":false,\"classId\":1,\"parentId\":1},{\"id\":1060,\"name\":\"Roleplay\",\"slug\":\"roleplay\",\"isClass\":false,\"classId\":1,\"parentId\":1},{\"id\":1011,\"name\":\"Map \u0026 Minimap\",\"slug\":\"map-minimap\",\"isClass\":false,\"classId\":1,\"parentId\":1},{\"id\":1050,\"name\":\"Jewelcrafting\",\"slug\":\"jewelcrafting\",\"isClass\":false,\"classId\":1,\"parentId\":1015},{\"id\":1031,\"name\":\"Development Tools\",\"slug\":\"development-tools\",\"isClass\":false,\"classId\":1,\"parentId\":1},{\"id\":1037,\"name\":\"Raid Frames\",\"slug\":\"raid-frames\",\"isClass\":false,\"classId\":1,\"parentId\":1016},{\"id\":1054,\"name\":\"Tailoring\",\"slug\":\"tailoring\",\"isClass\":false,\"classId\":1,